<div class="game_area_description" id="game_area_description">
 <h2>
  About This Game
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <strong>
   Fishing Inc
  </strong>
  is an addictive
  <strong>
   incremental
  </strong>
  <strong>
   fishing
  </strong>
  game! Catch fish, earn cash, and unlock powerful skills. Master new ponds, fill your Fish Log with Legendary catches, and become the ultimate angler.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag">
  Catch Fish!
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Travel to many of the locations and catch all the fish in the areas! To catch fish you will need to click till you reach the goal target before you lose the fish!
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="394" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4126480/extras/b6038575a3ce2ec7692773c1b7f52fc8.poster.avif?t=1776187675" width="704">
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4126480/extras/b6038575a3ce2ec7692773c1b7f52fc8.webm?t=1776187675" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
