   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag">
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag">
  Log Your Catches
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Over time you will get better at catching certain species of fish, you will learn their tricks and it will let you catch bigger and higher quality fish! You will discover many fish species as you travel trough the fishing locations!
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="392" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4126480/extras/3149320ed014c31c05dc069f033b4929.poster.avif?t=1776187675" width="702">
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4126480/extras/3149320ed014c31c05dc069f033b4929.webm?t=1776187675" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4126480/extras/3149320ed014c31c05dc069f033b4929.mp4?t=1776187675" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag">
  Upgrades
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  To become the best fisherman you will need all the best gear and upgrades, once you come back from your fishing trips you can spend your hard earned money on many upgrades that will help you catch bigger and more exotic fish
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="392" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4126480/extras/a7746e859efcd50203ebc4a5beaaa528.poster.avif?t=1776187675" width="700">
