<div class="game_area_description" id="game_area_description">
 <h2>
  About This Game
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="582" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/37e181a6adef0ff5fbff39dbbd12e42d.poster.avif?t=1776180058" width="1170">
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/37e181a6adef0ff5fbff39dbbd12e42d.webm?t=1776180058" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/37e181a6adef0ff5fbff39dbbd12e42d.mp4?t=1776180058" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag" style="text-align: center">
  Mine Gold Like During the Real Gold Rush!
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="496" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/ea2d9d28f2c8049e0a6dbe5f99071218.poster.avif?t=1776180058" width="1170">
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/ea2d9d28f2c8049e0a6dbe5f99071218.webm?t=1776180058" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/ea2d9d28f2c8049e0a6dbe5f99071218.mp4?t=1776180058" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Experience a gold mining process inspired by historical methods from the gold rush era.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Break rocks, collect ore, and separate gold from the soil using various tools and machines. Then smelt it into gold bars that you can sell at the bank.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  During the game you will find different forms of gold:
 </p>
 <ul class="bb_ul">
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    gold dust
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    gold flakes
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    gold nuggets
   </p>
  </li>
 </ul>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Each type has a different value and requires the proper refining process. As you progress through the game, you will unlock better tools and mining techniques.
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag" style="text-align: center">
  A System of Mines to Discover
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="496" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/11bac16fee7b4e54c860c78383cdf39b.poster.avif?t=1776180058" width="1170">
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/11bac16fee7b4e54c860c78383cdf39b.webm?t=1776180058" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/11bac16fee7b4e54c860c78383cdf39b.mp4?t=1776180058" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  In the game you can discover and explore a total of 9 mines.
 </p>
 <ul class="bb_ul">
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    5 small mines for quick expeditions
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    3 medium mines with branching tunnels
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    1 large multi-level mine
   </p>
  </li>
 </ul>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Each mine has its own unique atmosphere and several to dozens of segments to discover.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Working in a mine is dangerous. If you do not place supports correctly, tunnels may collapse. Build reinforcement structures, expand your infrastructure, and explore deeper underground.
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag" style="text-align: center">
  Upgrade Tools and Equipment
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="496" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/691aa9fbc90c7fce792c9949a6fb6801.poster.avif?t=1776180058" width="1170">
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/691aa9fbc90c7fce792c9949a6fb6801.webm?t=1776180058" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/691aa9fbc90c7fce792c9949a6fb6801.mp4?t=1776180058" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Your tools determine how fast and efficiently you can mine gold.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Create upgraded versions of your equipment and enhance them using rare materials and gemstones.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Possible upgrades include:
 </p>
 <ul class="bb_ul">
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    increased tool durability
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    faster resource extraction
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    ability to break harder rock
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    additional equipment upgrades
   </p>
  </li>
 </ul>
 <h2 class="bb_tag" style="text-align: center">
  Alaska, 1896 – A Rich Storyline
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="496" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/d62688db21f7e672432750efb72b1775.poster.avif?t=1776180058" width="1170">
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/d62688db21f7e672432750efb72b1775.webm?t=1776180058" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/d62688db21f7e672432750efb72b1775.mp4?t=1776180058" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Thousands of people arrive in northern America in search of fortune. Most will return empty-handed. Only a few will make history. Maybe you will be one of them.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  In Alaska Gold Fever you start as an ordinary gold prospector with simple tools and a big dream. Explore the wild lands of Alaska, mine gold, hunt, develop your businesses, and build an empire at the edge of 19th-century civilization.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  In the game you can expect many interesting and engaging storylines as well as unusual characters, such as the Pastor. A large number of fascinating stories and quests await you.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  The game offers:
 </p>
 <ul class="bb_ul">
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    a main storyline
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    side quests
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    hidden treasures
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    mysterious locations
   </p>
  </li>
 </ul>
 <h2 class="bb_tag" style="text-align: center">
  Crafting and Survival
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="496" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/819f4208e4e48f098bd638f92200355f.poster.avif?t=1776180058" width="1170">
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/819f4208e4e48f098bd638f92200355f.webm?t=1776180058" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/819f4208e4e48f098bd638f92200355f.mp4?t=1776180058" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Life in Alaska requires strategy and proper preparation.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Gather resources and craft useful items in different workshops such as:
 </p>
 <ul class="bb_ul">
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    tool workshop
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    carpentry workshop
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    fur workshop
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    campfire and kitchen
   </p>
  </li>
 </ul>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Preparing meals and resting provides bonuses that increase work efficiency, cold resistance, and character stamina.
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag" style="text-align: center">
  Hunt Wild Animals
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="496" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/0581468270afeb05aaf198b91dd7bfa1.poster.avif?t=1776180058" width="1170">
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/0581468270afeb05aaf198b91dd7bfa1.webm?t=1776180058" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/0581468270afeb05aaf198b91dd7bfa1.mp4?t=1776180058" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  The wild nature of Alaska is both a threat and a valuable source of resources.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  By hunting animals you can obtain:
 </p>
 <ul class="bb_ul">
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    meat
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    hides
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    furs
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    hunting trophies
   </p>
  </li>
 </ul>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  The quality of the materials you obtain depends on the weapon used and your hunting skills.
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag" style="text-align: center">
  Fight Extreme Cold
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="496" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/bf66864e0eb08602ceccb7d3631af978.poster.avif?t=1776180058" width="1170">
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/bf66864e0eb08602ceccb7d3631af978.webm?t=1776180058" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/bf66864e0eb08602ceccb7d3631af978.mp4?t=1776180058" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  The deeper you venture into the Alaskan wilderness, the lower the temperature becomes.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  To survive in the extreme climate you must:
 </p>
 <ul class="bb_ul">
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    wear warmer clothing
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    prepare proper meals
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    manage your energy and stamina
   </p>
  </li>
 </ul>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Lack of preparation can quickly end your expedition.
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag" style="text-align: center">
  Build Your Own Businesses
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="496" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/f749a3f331bfb8104433832d21af4d11.poster.avif?t=1776180058" width="1170">
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/f749a3f331bfb8104433832d21af4d11.webm?t=1776180058" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/f749a3f331bfb8104433832d21af4d11.mp4?t=1776180058" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Gold mining is only the beginning. You can develop different ventures and build your own economic empire:
 </p>
 <ul class="bb_ul">
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    new mines
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    farms producing food and milk
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    a hotel for travelers and gold prospectors
   </p>
  </li>
 </ul>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Hire workers, manage production, and expand your enterprises.
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag" style="text-align: center">
  Automate Your Mines
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="496" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/f07f41321dea620949ae83f1ca402ef2.poster.avif?t=1776180058" width="1170">
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/f07f41321dea620949ae83f1ca402ef2.webm?t=1776180058" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1674200/extras/f07f41321dea620949ae83f1ca402ef2.mp4?t=1776180058" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  The largest mines can be transformed into real enterprises.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Hire miners who will work for you and generate a steady income.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  This allows you to focus on exploration, business development, and discovering new lands.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
</div>
